00", "committee": "SJU", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sju28.mp3", "start_seconds": 2450.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2010-02-25T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "SJU", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sju28.mp3", "start_seconds": 2450.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2010-03-02T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "SEN", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sen30.mp3", "start_seconds": 6995.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2010-03-02T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "SEN", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sen30.mp3", "start_seconds": 6995.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2010-03-02T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "SEN", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sen30.mp3", "start_seconds": 6995.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2010-03-02T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "SEN", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2010/sen30.mp3", "start_seconds": 6995.0}], "bill_versions": [{"bill_id": 1759, "bill_version_id": 10794, "bill_version": "Introduced", "bill_version_date": "2010-01-21T11:45:01.127-06:00", "bill_text": "FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to limit the source of recovery in certain civil actions for childhood sexual abuse injuries. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That \u00a7 26-10-25 be amended to read as follows: 26-10-25. Any civil action based on intentional conduct brought by any person for recovery of damages for injury suffered as a result of childhood sexual abuse shall be commenced within three years of the act alleged to have caused the injury or condition, or three years of the time the victim discovered or reasonably should have discovered that the injury or condition was caused by the act, whichever period expires later. However, no person who has reached the age of twenty-five years may recover damages from any person or entity other than the person who perpetrated the actual act of sexual abuse. 180 copies of this document were printed by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.052 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes."}, {"bill_id": 1759, "bill_version_id": 12053, "bill_version": "House Judiciary Engrossed", "bill_version_date": "2010-02-10T13:40:18.987-06:00", "bill_text": "FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to limit the source of recovery in certain civil actions for childhood sexual abuse injuries. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That \u00a7 26-10-25 be amended to read as follows: 26-10-25. Any civil action based on intentional conduct brought by any person for recovery of damages for injury suffered as a result of childhood sexual abuse shall be commenced within three years of the act alleged to have caused the injury or condition, or three years of the time the victim discovered or reasonably should have discovered that the injury or condition was caused by the act, whichever period expires later. However, no person who has reached the age of thirty-five years may recover damages from any person or entity other than the person who perpetrated the actual act of sexual abuse. 180 copies of this document were printed by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.052 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes."}, {"bill_id": 1759, "bill_version_id": 13266, "bill_version": "Senate Engrossed", "bill_version_date": "2010-03-02T16:48:09.83-06:00", "bill_text": "FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to limit the source of recovery in certain civil actions for childhood sexual abuse injuries. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That \u00a7 26-10-25 be amended to read as follows: 26-10-25. Any civil action based on intentional conduct brought by any person for recovery of damages for injury suffered as a result of childhood sexual abuse shall be commenced within three years of the act alleged to have caused the injury or condition, or three years of the time the victim discovered or reasonably should have discovered that the injury or condition was caused by the act, whichever period expires later. However, no person who has reached the age of forty years may recover damages from any person or entity other than the person who perpetrated the actual act of sexual abuse. 180 copies of this document were printed by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.052 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes."}, {"bill_id": 1759, "bill_version_id": 13541, "bill_version": "Enrolled", "bill_version_date": "2010-03-08T09:32:09.357-06:00", "bill_text": ""}], "amendments": [], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 1759, "action_date": "2010-01-21T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 10821, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/10821.pdf", "status_text": "First read in House and referred to", "journal_page": 147, "committee_id_action": 86, "committee_id_assigned": 82, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 1759, "action_date": "2010-02-10T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 11779, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/11779.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for hearing", "journal_page": 0, "committee_id_action": 82, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 1759, "action_date": "2010-02-10T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 12039, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/12039.pdf", "status_text": "Motion to amend", "journal_page": 0, "committee_id_action": 82, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 1759, "action_date": "2010-02-10T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 12039, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/12039.pdf", "status_text": "Do Pass Amended", "journal_page": 344, "committee_id_acti